                <note rend="inline" type="source">821.6363/1059: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Colombia</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Caffery</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Bogotá</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-02-20T15:00:00-05:00"
                            >February 20, 1931—3 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received 5:25 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>18. My telegram number 12, February 11, 6 p.m.<note n="16" xml:id="d21fn16">Not
                        printed.</note> Olaya sent a message to the House Wednesday urging deputies
                    to expedite consideration of the oil bill. Up to last night House had approved
                    19 articles.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Caffery</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
